## Question

What is good about kids?

* Can do whatever they want (Really?)
* They're the best
* Get free breakfast, lunch, dinner
* Don't have to buy anything
* Get to play all day
* Happy
* Quick to forgive and forget
* Good at making friends
* Listening to instructions

